== Umugambi ==
Nana Kwame, umwimukira utemewe n'amategeko wo muri [[Gana]] ukorera mu [[Bwongereza]] wabuze byose kubera ubuhemu, asanga yatangiriye kuri odyssey ku giti cye cyo kwivumbura. Yambuwe ibintu hafi ya byose , aho atuye, ndetse n'icyubahiro, agomba kubona inzira anyuze mu butaka butamenyerewe bw'abimuwe kandi batagaragara. Ni muri iyi saha y'umwijima, ku batishoboye cyane, ubuzima bwe buhinduka mu buryo butunguranye iyo abonye ubwiza n'urukundo bikura mu butayu bwa beto. Nubwo indorerwamo ari Shauna, ahita amenya ko ibyahise bishobora kuba gereza twaremye kubwubwenge bwacu. Mu gufasha kuvana Shauna muri gereza ye ni bwo yaje kurekurwa wenyine. 

